Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of remote sensing software packages for analyzing and visualizing remotely sensed data, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques. The focus on image fusion technologies and quality evaluation suggests that the paper may also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Finally, the development of a program for image fusion and classification may also involve machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
